reviewText: My kids (all ages) love this show.  They love learning all the different animals.
I love the wild animal baby collection my daughter learns so much from them.
Great value!! My Grandson really enjoys this series. The content is excellent!
My son loves the animals babies
It is wonderful just wish I could find them all
Nice deal. My kids enjoy this show and now we have the whole series so we don't have to watch the same three episodes all the time (we had another DVD)

Although there are lots of channels about animals such animal channel and BBC, etc. I think they are for older kids for 7+. But Wild Animal Baby Explorers complete set is definitely best for baby to toddler to watch. Very educational and fun.
